description: [``botocore``] Add support for customizing time zone for backup window in backup plan rules.
[``botocore``] This release enables AWS Compute Optimizer to analyze and generate licensing optimization recommendations for sql server running on EC2 instances.
[``botocore``] Documentation updates for permissions and links.
[``botocore``] Remove incorrect regex enforcement on pagination tokens.
[``botocore``] Service Quotas now supports viewing the applied quota value and requesting a quota increase for a specific resource in an AWS account.

[``botocore``] WorkSpaces Web now enables Admins to configure which cookies are synchronized from an end-user's local browser to the in-session browser. In conjunction with a browser extension, this feature enables enhanced Single-Sign On capability by reducing the number of times an end-user has to authenticate.
